title: FORECLOSURE SALE By order of lien: Accepting bids at PO
text:
FORECLOSURE SALE By order of lien: Accepting bids at PO ad date: 10/10/2015 
FORECLOSURE SALE By order of lien: Accepting bids at PO Box 7682 Brookings, OR 97415 RE: 2002 Newmark trailer (July 2015) VIN# 1N8KS332X20079217) 2010 owner(s) unknown, DMV unable to identify owner or lienholder, abandoned on real property,16104 Kings Way, Harbor, OR. Contact Carousel Petroleum for viewing appointment. Bidding starts Oct. 15 to Oct. 22 at 4pm. We reserve the right to refuse any and all bids. Storage, towing and court fees applicable. Publish October 10, 14 & 17, 2015 No. 71111627
